  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <h3 data-mpa-powered-by=\"yiban.io\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42421875\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" style=\"width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/UicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtib0lMBYthicYUibKSX6cPpEdaJmZWzgwh82SQrQMibTZPlJMLKJxlsdBMQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"247\" data-backw=\"578\" data-backh=\"245\" data-imgfileid=\"505177250\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=effab547&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtib0lMBYthicYUibKSX6cPpEdaJmZWzgwh82SQrQMibTZPlJMLKJxlsdBMQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-src=\"\"></span></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <h3 style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n   <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <div data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <div data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n      <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n       <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin-top: -1.2em;margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;outline: 0px;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新智元报道 &nbsp;</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">编辑：元宇</span></span></p>\n  <div powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"outline:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;\">\n   <div style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\">\n    <p style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n    <h5 style=\"padding:10px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;margin-right:8px;margin-left:8px;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;word-break:break-all !important;margin-top:10px;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\">【新智元导读】</span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Meta腾出CoWoS排产「让路」，加上台积电的积极扩产，2026年谷歌把TPU的「算力水龙头」拧到最大，预期产能飙升至430万颗，猛攻英伟达CUDA护城河。</span></span></strong></span></h5>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91zz7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">430万颗！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot915bx\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot915bx\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">2026年的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot915bx\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">TPU最新产能数据曝光。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91nyn\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">该数据来自Global Semi Research（全球半导体研究）最新的一项独立研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9tul\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">该项研究将谷歌2026年的TPU产能数据更新如下：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2026年TPU总产能将达到430万颗；按型号拆分V6为15万颗，V7为135万颗，V8AX为240万颗，V8X为40万颗。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7409326424870466\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1158\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1158\" data-height=\"858\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"416\" data-imgfileid=\"505177243\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b5582cf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtWFlK5pdibJXoWpV4HouUTHlvoF7LcljiaYAWYWx7w6grpdLpHzu3KJcg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91mzj\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中，V8AX和V8X总计280万颗，占比约65%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91mzj\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这表明谷歌在产能布局上，将优先保障新一代TPU（可能用于Gemini模型或云服务）的产能，而V6/V7为库存或低端市场，可能用于过渡或特定应用。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91zig\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">该研究指出，谷歌TPU产能原本仅略高于300万颗，此次增长到430万颗主要来自两大因素：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一，Meta下调了自研芯片产量，并将释放出来的CoWoS产能转向TPU制造；Meta也希望通过此举锁定/确保TPU供应；</span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二，台积电扩充CoWoS产能，新增产能预计将于2026年8月投产。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot911b0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这430万颗TPU芯片，395万颗（92%）由台积电代工，其余35万颗（8%）可能由日月光（ASE）外包。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7548500881834215\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1134\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1134\" data-height=\"856\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"424\" data-imgfileid=\"505177246\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17102d25&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqticLVy3KelgN8FyJXy27ycooNZaPrymB3D6kcGt7zicdI3wXfKzCqPTpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot919ea\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">制造商分布，突出供应链依赖台积电。台积电是先进封装（CoWoS）的关键供应商，由此也暴露出谷歌TPU交付仍面临先进封装产能短缺的风险。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot916jk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">谷歌的TPU产能从原本的略超300万颗大幅上调至430万颗（增长了43.33%），也显示出它的雄心：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不仅通过自研TPU降低成本（据分析，每FLOP成本比英伟达GB200/300低20-50%），还要挑战英伟达在AI芯片市场的霸主地位。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91s5c\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">虽然谷歌TPU的需求强劲，如Anthropic等客户兴趣高涨，但受制于CoWoS封装、内存供应短缺、英伟达竞争等因素，业界对其2026年TPU产量的各种预测通常低于430万颗。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">Meta「割肉」助攻</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mk0rpjbs21gq\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91vj0\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">先进封装（以CoWoS为代表</span></span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0rpjbj1tr5\"><span leaf=\"\">）<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">是AI加速器交付链条中的关键环节。</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9q7c\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">它虽然不是芯片产能，却是其「出货闸门」，也是卡住TPU供应的最后一道关口：</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"line-height: 1.75;letter-spacing: 1px;word-break: break-word;color: rgb(91, 91, 91);border-left: 8px solid rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.3);border-radius: 5px;background: rgba(158, 158, 158, 0.1);padding-top: 24px;padding-bottom: 24px;padding-right: 8px;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n   <p style=\"font-size: 15px;margin: 0 8px;padding-left: 8px;padding-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">先进封装/集成决定了芯片最终能不能变成可用的加速卡/模块。</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91n77\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">黄仁勋曾表示，近年来先进封装产能虽在快速扩张（两年内显著放大），但仍是制约项。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9d1m\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，一旦Meta这样的大客户把原本锁定的CoWoS排产转移出来，将直接影响谷歌TPU</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9d1m\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">的</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9d1m\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">可交付数量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91o4p\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">当然，这也可能带有一点「供应锁定」的意味：把资源转过去，等于把未来TPU的交付也一起锁住。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2924731182795699\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"930\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"930\" data-height=\"272\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"164\" data-imgfileid=\"505177244\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c97595cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtrnHmjZpf21fUK7XdTnx6Db2ufC4ciaffDdtlcofUMK8KSS4Fzh8o8LQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9vgx\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据路透社援引知情人士称，去年8月，Meta与谷歌云达成了一项为期6年、价值超过100亿美元的云计算协议，用于支撑其AI基础设施。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9x51\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">去年11月，Meta与谷歌洽谈，计划2027年起在自己的数据中心使用谷歌的TPU，并可能最早在2026年通过谷歌云租用TPU算力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot95ui\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">与此同时，谷歌也在进行一个名为「TorchTPU」的内部项目，目标是让TPU更好兼容PyTorch，而Meta正是PyTorch的主要支持者。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9gj1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一系列的交易与合作所透露的信息不仅是TPU采购，也预示着两家将在AI基建层面更紧密合作，也使得Meta的CoWoS排产转移与谷歌TPU交付量上调二者的关联顺理成章。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;text-align:center;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.26993865030674846\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1304\" style=\"background-color: transparent;width: 100%;\" data-width=\"1304\" data-height=\"352\" data-backw=\"562\" data-backh=\"152\" data-imgfileid=\"505177245\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d543c10c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3Spv8cZIZ7WYgABwLa0sqtwJgib6DL2JjlP1QTbhlXiaEmPLGicyT9sg5ibs23EfkaaeBlBMFyJgZYAg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91dtk\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据路透社报道，Meta自去年3月已经开始测试其首款自主研发的AI训练芯片，并计划在测试顺利后扩大规模。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9ts7\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">开发自研芯片是Meta长期计划的一部分，旨在降低其庞大的基础设施成本，并减少对英伟达等外部芯片供应商的依赖。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9hx4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">从某种意义上说，Meta自研芯片阵线的收缩与「让路」，反倒成全了谷歌TPU的扩产计划。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5267857142857143\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"112\" style=\"width: 85px;height: 40px;\" data-imgfileid=\"505095291\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6568e90c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3uEdSPKrwGNmZEOaaGyzVvZ8dTtE9jU1rFsda3llYbCZpmWfiazUYjWBLTGvlPpXucH8Q0lEUJN3Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:1px;font-size:19px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">台积电扩充产能</span></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9zm3\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">在AI芯片「强需求、强扩产」的周期中，面对客户不断追加和锁定其对于先进芯片的产能需求，台积电也一直在持续加码后端产线（CoWoS）建设以缩小缺口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9nra\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">台积电曾在2025Q1财报电话会中提到：由于客户强需求，将「努力在2025年把CoWoS产能翻倍」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91cqr\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">台积电董事长魏哲家也在2025Q2财报电话会上表示，当前以及2026年都在努力缩小供需缺口，并通过在后端建设许多新设施来增加CoWoS产能以支持客户。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9wur\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">据TrendForce报道，行业预估台积电计划把CoWoS月产能从7.5–8万片/月，拉升至2026年末12–13万片/月。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot91gcv\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">所以，430万颗TPU不只是「产能数字」，更像一张2026年的「算力通行证」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9xy4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">随着谷歌TPU产量的快速增加，Anthropic、Meta、</span>Safe Superintelligence（SSI）<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">、xAI、OpenAI等</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9xy4\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">TPU</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mk0q6ot9xy4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">客户的名单也在不断扩大，预示着这些AI巨头们为了摆脱过于依赖单一供应商的风险，开始联手重塑AI算力格局。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\">参考资料：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://substack.com/@globalsemiresearch/note/c-195015090?utm_source=notes-share-action&amp;r=4k4uta\" target=\"_blank\">https://substack.com/@globalsemiresearch/note/c-195015090?utm_source=notes-share-action&amp;r=4k4uta</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "谷歌预计 2026 年 TPU 产能将飙升至 430 万颗，主要得益于 Meta“割肉”让出 CoWoS 产能和台积电的扩产，此举被视为对英伟达 CUDA 生态的有力挑战。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "谷歌预计 2026 年 TPU 产能将飙升至 430 万颗，主要得益于 Meta“割肉”让出 CoWoS 产能和台积电的扩产，此举被视为对英伟达 CUDA 生态的有力挑战。",
  "summary": "新智元报道指出，Global Semi Research 最新研究显示，谷歌 2026 年 TPU 总产能预计将达到 430 万颗，其中 V8AX 和 V8X 将占主导。这一显著增长主要归因于两方面：一是 Meta 调整自研芯片产量，将其原本锁定的 CoWoS 产能转向 TPU 制造，以期锁定未来 TPU 供应并加强与谷歌的 AI 基础设施合作；二是台积电持续扩充 CoWoS 先进封装产能，预计新增产能将于 2026 年 8 月投产。文章分析认为，谷歌此举不仅旨在降低自身成本，更重要的是挑战英伟达在 AI 芯片市场的统治地位。尽管 TPU 需求强劲，但供应链仍面临先进封装和内存供应等短缺风险。同时，谷歌通过“TorchTPU”项目提升 TPU 对 PyTorch 的兼容性，并与 Meta 等 AI 巨头联手，共同寻求 AI 算力格局的多元化。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
